==[[HP:0003743]]==
{{Infobox HPO
| hpoId = HP:0003743
| 名称 = Genetic anticipation
| 定义 = A mode of inheritance in which the severity of a disorder increases or the age of onset decreases as the disorder is passed from one generation to the next.
| 中文译名 = 遗传早现
| 中文定义 = #####
}}


==[[HP:0003744]]==
{{Infobox HPO
| hpoId = HP:0003744
| 名称 = Genetic anticipation with paternal anticipation bias
| 定义 = A type of genetic anticipation observed predominantly upon transmission from affected males.
| 中文译名 = 偏向父系传递的遗传早现
| 中文定义 = #####
}}

==[[HP:0003745]]==
{{Infobox HPO
| hpoId = HP:0003745
| 名称 = Sporadic
| 定义 = Cases of the disease in question occur without a previous family history, i.e., as isolated cases without being transmitted from a parent and without other siblings being affected.
| 中文译名 = 散发的
| 中文定义 = #####
}}


==[[HP:0010982]]==
{{Infobox HPO
| hpoId = HP:0010982
| 名称 = Polygenic inheritance
| 定义 = A type of multifactorial inheritance governed by the simultaneous action of many (more than three) gene loci.
| 中文译名 = 多基因遗传
| 中文定义 = #####
}}


==[[HP:0010983]]==
{{Infobox HPO
| hpoId = HP:0010983
| 名称 = Oligogenic inheritance
| 定义 = A type of multifactorial inheritance governed by the simultaneous action of a few gene loci. It is recommended this term be used for traits governed by three loci, although it is noted that usage of this term in the literature is not uniform.
| 中文译名 = 寡基因遗传
| 中文定义 = #####
}}


==[[HP:0010984]]==
{{Infobox HPO
| hpoId = HP:0010984
| 名称 = Digenic inheritance
| 定义 = A type of multifactorial inheritance governed by the simultaneous action of two gene loci.
| 中文译名 = 双基因遗传
| 中文定义 = #####
}}


==[[HP:0010985]]==
{{Infobox HPO
| hpoId = HP:0010985
| 名称 = Gonosomal inheritance
| 定义 = A mode of inheritance that is observed for traits related to a gene encoded on the sex chromosomes.
| 中文译名 = 性连锁遗传
| 中文定义 = #####
}}


==[[HP:0012274]]==
{{Infobox HPO
| hpoId = HP:0012274
| 名称 = Autosomal dominant inheritance with paternal imprinting
| 定义 = A type of autosomal dominant inheritance involving a gene that is imprinted with paternal silencing.
| 中文译名 = 父源印记基因常染色体显性遗传
| 中文定义 = #####
}}

