{{Infobox HPO
| hpoId = HP:0012275
| 名称 = Autosomal dominant inheritance with maternal imprinting
| 定义 = A type of autosomal dominant inheritance involving a gene that is imprinted with maternal silencing.
| 中文译名 = 母源印记基因常染色体显性遗传
| 中文定义 = #####
}}